708133f-b.title: Manhattan: 3rd Avenue - 90th Street
708133f-b.text:
Jacob Ruppert's Brewery; bottling department, one of the oldest
buildings, N.E. corner of Third Avenue and 90th Street.
MT Ruppert, in addition to his brewing activities, is owner of
the New York Yankees, a professional baseball club in the
Amwerican L6agu6.
June 26, 1931.
